 The Anteaters were led by sophomore center Allah-mi Basheer, who scored a 
career-high 19 points. Junior forward Jinelle Williams, former Brea-Olinda High 
School player, added 17 points and 11 rebounds. Senior guard Karie Yoshioka, a 
graduate of El Toro High School, scored 16 points. 
</P>
