the 10, two were discharged, three are undergoing proceedings that could result 
in discharges, one was discharged for unrelated misconduct, one received 
administrative pun ishment and two are awaiting a decision on possible 
punishment, the Marine Corps said. The status of the 10th was not disclosed. 
