Inc. in Tustin, succeeding John W. Adams, who remains as chairman.Matros, who 
is also the company's president and chief operating officer, joined Care 
Enterprises in 1987 as its executive vice president of operations. He has been 
a director of the company since November, 1991, and president and chief 
operating officer since September, 1991. Previously, Matros was with Beverly 
Enterprises for four years. Care Enterprises, a provider of inpatient and 
