<TEXT>
<P>
 One person was killed and another seriously injured Thursday in a head-on 
collision on Sierra Highway, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 Robert Almy, 54, of Canyon Country, was driving northbound on Sierra Highway, 
just north of Scherzinger Lane, when his car crossed the center line about 7:45 
a.m. and collided with a southbound vehicle, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 Almy was freed from his vehicle by county firefighters. 
