 Muffler shop owner -- A story Wednesday about a crackdown on falsified smog 
certificates incorrectly stated that Benito Ciano had been arrested. Charges 
were filed only against Ciano's business, Doug's Muffler and Brake Inc., said 
Deputy Dist. Atty. Robert C. Gannon Jr. 
</P>
